msgid ""
"For more information, see the <a href=\":views\">online documentation "
"for the Views module</a>."
msgstr ""
"Daugiau informacijos rasite <a href=\":views\">Views modulio "
"internetinėje dokumentacijoje</a>."

msgid ""
"Contributed projects that support the Views module can be found in the "
"<a href=\":node\">online documentation for Views-related contributed "
"modules</a>."
msgstr ""
"Prisidėjusios projektus, kurie palaiko Views modulį, galite rasti <a "
"href=\":node\">interneto dokumentacijoje apie Views moduliams skirtus "
