msgid ""
"<strong>If the old site has private files</strong>, a copy of its "
"files directory must also be accessible on the host of this new site."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Jei senajame tinklalapyje yra privatūs failai</strong>, jų "
"katalogo kopija taip pat turi būti pasiekiama naujojo tinklalapio "
