"<strong>@sitemap, line @line</strong>: The path <em>@path</em> needs "
"to start with a '/'."
msgstr ""
"<strong>@sitemap, eilutė @line</strong>: Kelias <em>@path</em> turi "
"prasidėti ženklu '/'."

msgid ""
"<strong>@sitemap, line @line</strong>: The priority setting "
"<em>@priority</em> for path <em>@path</em> is incorrect. Set the "
"priority from 0.0 to 1.0."
msgstr ""
"<strong>@sitemap, eilutė @line</strong>: Prioriteto nustatymas "
"<em>@priority</em> keliui <em>@path</em> yra neteisingas. Nustatykite "
"prioritetą nuo 0.0 iki 1.0."

msgid ""
"<strong>@sitemap, line @line</strong>: The changefreq setting "
"<em>@changefreq</em> for path <em>@path</em> is incorrect. The "
"following are the correct values: <em>@changefreq_options</em>."
msgstr ""
"<strong>@sitemap, eilutė @line</strong>: Keitimo dažnio nustatymas "
"<em>@changefreq</em> keliui <em>@path</em> yra neteisingas. Teisingos "
"reikšmės yra šios: <em>@changefreq_options</em>."

